"""
        Test that a DeviceCredential struct missing device serial number data
        can be written to a data stream.
        """
credential = objects.DeviceCredential(password='secret', device_identifier=
    'devID2233', network_identifier='netID9000', machine_identifier=
    'machineID1', media_identifier='mediaID313')
stream = utils.BytearrayStream()
credential.write(stream)
self.assertEqual(len(self.encoding_missing_device_serial_number), len(stream))
self.assertEqual(str(self.encoding_missing_device_serial_number), str(stream))
